R|name=[[Juan Escobar (Paraguayan footballer)|Juan Escobar]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=25|nat=MEX|name=[[Roberto Alvarado]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=29|nat=MEX|name=Santiago Gim\u00e9nez|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=30|nat=MEX|name=Andr\u00e9s Gudi\u00f1o|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=31|nat=MEX|name=[[Orbel\u00edn Pineda]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=33|nat=MEX|name=[[Sebasti\u00e1n Jurado]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs end}}\n{{For|recent transfers|List of Mexican football transfers summer 2019}}\n\n===Out on loan===\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Richard Ruiz]]|pos=DF|other=at [[Deportivo Toluca F.C.|Toluca]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=CAN|name=[[Stephen Eust\u00e1quio]]|other=at [[F.C. Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira|Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ARG|name=[[Guillermo Mat\u00edas Fern\u00e1ndez|Guillermo Fern\u00e1ndez]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Boca Juniors]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ARG|name=[[Walter Montoya]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Racing Club de Avellaneda|Racing Club]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Javier Salas (footballer)|Javier Salas]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Club Puebla|Puebla]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=Ra\u00fal Varela|pos=MF|other=at [[Club Ca\u00f1oneros Marina|Marina]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ECU|name=[[Brayan Angulo Tenorio|Brayan Angulo]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Club Tijuana|Tijuana]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=COL|name=[[Andr\u00e9s Renter\u00eda]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Rionegro \u00c1guilas]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Mart\u00edn Eduardo Z\u00fa\u00f1iga|Mart\u00edn Z\u00fa\u00f1iga]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Celaya F.C.|Celaya]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Reserve teams===\n\n{{Main|Cruz Azul Reserves}}\n\n;[[Cruz Azul Hidalgo]]\n:Reserve team that plays in the [[Liga Premier de M\u00e9xico|Liga Premier]] in the third level of the Mexican league system.\n\n;[[Cruz Azul Lagunas]]\n:Reserve team that plays in the [[Tercera Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico|Liga TDP]], the fifth level of the Mexican league system.\n\n=